程序包 com.academic_assistant.controller

类 CourseController

java.lang.Object
com.academic_assistant.controller.CourseController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/courses") public class CourseController extends Object
This class serves as the controller for managing courses within the system. It handles HTTP requests related to courses, such as retrieving courses, enrolling in courses, exiting courses, searching for courses, and providing course recommendations.
